{
  "stem": "9701.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were afraid that they might catch fire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But they vandalized the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "For instance, on top of the synagogue there were the two tablets of Moses.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they were torn down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They vandalized the inside, broke the windows.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I learned subsequently that they took the Torah scrolls out of the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the men that we had seen marching down the street were taken to the next community to the railroad station there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And by the time they arrived there, the Torah scrolls were strung up open on the platform for them to see.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I was so traumatized by the events of that day, that I did not permit my mother or my aunt out of my sight.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "For instance, if one of us had to go to the bathroom, three of us went to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We could not get the windows replaced in our home, so we decided to stay at my aunt's house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we moved an extra bed into the bedroom so the three of us could sleep in the same room because I would not sleep alone in a room.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was absolutely no information about the men and boys who had been taken away for two weeks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was some food, of course, in my aunt's house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had some in our house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And while I don't remember it, I imagine we got the food from our house back over to my aunt's house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had some money, though the money-- and I don't quite know how that was-- but I know the money was confiscated.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were given an allowance every month.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't know what the amount was on which we lived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't really recall how that all happened and how we got the food.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
